Additionally, the paper discusses the use of distance metrics to compare traces of states and rewards, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the application of the approach to healthcare, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence to personalize health interventions, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
